Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:07.22,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}山寺鐘鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:16.74,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}お手で繋いで　皆帰ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:16.74,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}牽手同歸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:27.46,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}カラスと一緒に帰りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:27.46,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}烏鴉相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快點回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了  我要和仁村先生分手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被美羽甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的王子是仁村先生真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我送你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰姑娘不想被人看到魔法解除後的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:39.18,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}子供が帰った後からは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:39.18,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}兒童歸家後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:45.82,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}丸い大きなお月様
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:45.82,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}圓月當頭掛
