Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:52.41,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}小鳥入夢時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:59.94,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}空にはキラキラ銀色星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:59.94,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}天空閃銀星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  謝謝你  我非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  要洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽  今天好晚啊  怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密～是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以說悄悄話哦  園長這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不可以對小舅舅保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子是由秘密組成的哦  舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
